* kernel: userfaultfd bypasses tmpfs file permissions (CVE-2018-18397)

* kernel: Integer overflow in the alarm_timer_nsleep function
(CVE-2018-13053)

* kernel: NULL pointer dereference in xfs_da_shrink_inode function
(CVE-2018-13094)

